reviewText: I've never seen this dvd before and I never new that they had a dvd out anyway

I bought this DVD new and used for me and my sisters. We loved every minute of it. However I wish that it lastest abit longer than 30 minutes for the price of 20 bucks. But, I love the guys...they are cool, funny, and very talented. This documentary really does show  you how B5 all got started in the industry. :>)*
Purchased this for my daughter and niece. They loved it!  They watch it over and over again.

this dvd was a good documentary about the lives of dustin kelly patrick carnell and bryan breeding its has some humor some live shows and out takes of their christmas special even has some never before seen pics of them as little kids they interview the individual and they say things about each other shows them dancing everything its really good and i enjoyed it im sure it doesnt tell the whole story of how they got discovered they just say a "friend" but i kno they got family in the buisness this dvd deservies 5 stars
